---
// About User / Profile page
---

<div class="flex-1 flex flex-col overflow-hidden">
  <div class="flex-1 overflow-y-auto p-6">
    <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto space-y-8 content-stagger">
      <div class="border-b-2 border-[#13ec13] pb-4 mb-6">
        <h2 class="text-2xl md:text-3xl font-bold text-glow flex items-center gap-2">
          <span class="material-symbols-outlined">person</span>
          ABOUT_USER
        </h2>
        <p class="text-sm opacity-80 mt-1 font-mono-terminal">VAULT_DWELLER_PROFILE // CLEARANCE_LEVEL: 5</p>
      </div>

      <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-6">
        <div class="border border-[#13ec13]/30 p-4 rounded bg-[#13ec13]/5">
          <h3 class="text-sm font-bold border-b border-[#13ec13]/30 pb-2 mb-3 flex items-center gap-2">
            <span class="material-symbols-outlined text-base">badge</span>
            IDENTITY
          </h3>
          <div class="space-y-1 text-sm font-mono-terminal">
            <p><span class="opacity-60">USER_ID:</span> ADMIN_OVERRIDE</p>
            <p><span class="opacity-60">ROLE:</span> FULL_STACK_ENGINEER</p>
            <p><span class="opacity-60">SPECIAL:</span> 7 | 8 | 5 | 3 | 6 | 4</p>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="border border-[#13ec13]/30 p-4 rounded bg-[#13ec13]/5">
          <h3 class="text-sm font-bold border-b border-[#13ec13]/30 pb-2 mb-3 flex items-center gap-2">
            <span class="material-symbols-outlined text-base">location_on</span>
            LOCATION
          </h3>
          <div class="space-y-1 text-sm font-mono-terminal">
            <p><span class="opacity-60">REGION:</span> COMMONWEALTH</p>
            <p><span class="opacity-60">VAULT:</span> 111_RECON</p>
            <p><span class="opacity-60">STATUS:</span> ACTIVE</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="border border-[#13ec13]/30 p-4 rounded bg-black/40">
        <h3 class="text-sm font-bold border-b border-[#13ec13]/30 pb-2 mb-3 flex items-center gap-2">
          <span class="material-symbols-outlined text-base">description</span>
          BIO_LOG
        </h3>
        <p class="text-sm font-mono-terminal leading-relaxed opacity-90">
          &gt; SUBJECT ENTERED VAULT-TEC ARCHIVES 2075<br />
          &gt; SPECIALIZATION: WEB_DEV, UI_UX, WASTELAND_TECH<br /><br />
          Terminal operator with expertise in pre-war and post-war systems. Experienced in RobCo, General Atomics, and Vault-Tec protocols. Survived the Institute purge. Current assignment: maintain Termlink infrastructure for Commonwealth settlements.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>
